description:
Office Tab Enterprise v10.50

New features:
1. You can switch among languages directly on the Office Tab ribbon as follows. See screenshot: &lt;a href=&quot;
http://www.extendoffice.com/images/stories/shot-office-tab/office-tab-10.50/Office-tab-10.50-1.png&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; target=&quot;_NEW&quot;&gt;
http://www.extendoffice.com/images/stories/shot-office-tab/office-tab-10.50/Office-tab-10.50-1.png&lt;/a&gt;
2. Add the Close Left feature to the right-clicking menu: you can quickly close all tabs which locate on the left side of current tab. See screenshot: &lt;a href=&quot;
http://www.extendoffice.com/images/stories/shot-office-tab/office-tab-10.50/Office-tab-10.50-2.png&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; target=&quot;_NEW&quot;&gt;
http://www.extendoffice.com/images/stories/shot-office-tab/office-tab-10.50/Office-tab-10.50-2.png&lt;/a&gt;
3. Add the Close Right feature to the right-clicking menu: you can quickly close all tabs which locate on the right side of current tab. See screenshot: &lt;a href=&quot;
http://www.extendoffice.com/images/stories/shot-office-tab/office-tab-10.50/Office-tab-10.50-3.png&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; target=&quot;_NEW&quot;&gt;
http://www.extendoffice.com/images/stories/shot-office-tab/office-tab-10.50/Office-tab-10.50-3.png&lt;/a&gt;

Improvements:
1. Optimize the tab color in Office 2016.
2. Proofreading some interface language items.

Fixed:
1. Fixed: Word will crash with View Side by Side in Word 2013-16 versions.
2. Fixed: Inserting PowerPoint or Excel objects in other Office programs will cause abnormal problem.
3. Fixed: The Publisher icon is displayed as the Access icon in the Tab in Access 2010.
4. Fixed: Language cannot be changed when you clicking Options from the right-clicking menu and try to change the language in the Option setting center in Office 2010.
5. Fixed: The workbooks are modified or not which is not indicating correctly with * mark in Office Tab for Excel 2013-2016.
6. Fixed: Even though the Single-window mode has been enabled in Office Tab for Office 2013-2016, there are multiple Office windows when switching windows by using shortcuts Alt + Tab.
7. Fixed: In some Office applications, Office tab cannot switch among windows after document windows minimizing
